TitMainTitle: Group portrait of young women, possibly including seated: Marilyn Ware third from left, Lois Weaver Watson fifth from left, Frances Bell (Nunn) seventh from left, Marguerite Dodson wearing striped top third from right; and young men, including two wearing U.S. Navy sailor uniforms, and possibly Mozelle Thompson wearing bow tie facing away near center, gathered on and around striped furniture, in Loendi Club with sawdust on hardwood floors
